{"tid":1956852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢見民政署回覆音樂噴泉的文件","createTime":"2020-04-03T12:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T08:07:56.000Z","uid":236878,"like":48,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b25e7e0b98efa1eb90c8e8b9c5cf367a757083f2","tid":1956852,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">頭盔：以下內容係朋友發夢見到好嬲話我知 我代po 啫<br />\n如有雷同 實屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n我朋友話民政署有條67 叫中xG  （之前已經出撚哂名）<br />\n<br />\n回覆觀塘區議會查詢 <br />\n就話 嗱 15年呢就做咗個問卷調查 訪問咗八百幾個海濱公園的<span style=\"color: red;\">使用者</span>  當中都有超過四百幾個支持起咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果份所謂問卷調查 求其問個中學生都應該睇到有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.當中<span style=\"color: red;\">一半人唔撚係觀塘區居民嚟</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘩dllm咁都得 你不如訪問埋芝麻人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<del>不過可能真係有都唔出奇</del><br />\n<br />\n訪問「海濱使用者」有咩問題呢 <br />\n成件事就好似咁： <br />\n佢有1個口罩 想派畀人 <br />\n但係求其搵了個廢老 問佢要唔要口罩 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDllm老閪都答你要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無考慮埋其他觀塘居民意見 無考慮過必要性 無考慮其他更好方案(果陣未有疫情 所以口罩唔計住 但加設醫療設備 e.g.流動診所車 都好過on9噴泉n倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n3.成份問卷完全無提過造價大約要幾多 <br />\n明明應該起碼有一題係問人prefer起咩 畀幾個選擇<br />\n可能排1-5咁<br />\n但係完全無問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就話大部分人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌唔怪之得成份野唔敢公開啦 造到份問卷咁撚樣都係勉強過半支持 最後引用保蝗黨數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我真係好好奇民x聯個調查點造到85%支持？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪用你老味個屎忽計出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTu7Ogi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTu7Ogi.png&h=867923d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1719036061866d60ca2efd1048a90309d2899e4","tid":1956852,"uid":264245,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個政府都假既"},{"pid":"5095e9e82b8b2e9c5b57bcd686e665e3e507964e","tid":1956852,"uid":236878,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a1719036061866d60ca2efd1048a90309d2899e4","tid":1956852,"uid":264245,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個政府都假既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"學埋G共d野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f3029a1f9e8c0bb24ba3e13f5be5885d0ab80d","tid":1956852,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026159f7a260e51f05ff96916c601fdeaab25c0f","tid":1956852,"uid":3513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5095e9e82b8b2e9c5b57bcd686e665e3e507964e","tid":1956852,"uid":236878,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a1719036061866d60ca2efd1048a90309d2899e4","tid":1956852,"uid":264245,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個政府都假既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"